ileName":"18768915-2533-433f-a166-94ef17043fe6.jpg","locale":"ja","createdAt":"2024-07-03T22:22:22+00:00","updatedAt":"2024-07-03T22:22:22+00:00","version":1}}]},{"id":"151bca3e-db98-4ad2-8d8d-239943b91437","type":"manga","attributes":{"title":{"zh-ro":"Y\u01d2u Sh\u00f2u Y\u0101n"},"altTitles":[{"zh":"\u6709\u517d\u7109"},{"en":"Fabulous Beasts"},{"en":"There Are Beasts"},{"es-la":"Existen Bestias"},{"es-la":"Bestias Fabulosas"},{"vi":"C\u00f3 Linh Th\u00fa"},{"vi":"H\u1eefu Th\u00fa Y\u00ean"},{"pt-br":"Bestas Fabulosas"}],"description":{"en":"\"In this realm mythological creatures roam, descendant of the nine heavens they call home.\" \n\nSibuxiang, a mythical deer-man couch potato, is kicked out of heaven and assigned to support the mythological creatures wandering the human world. He meets and goes on adventures with his friends: the energetic, food loving Pixiu named Pipi, the fanatic moon bunny Tuye, the banished-from-heaven mouse brothers Jinjiao and Yinjiao, and many others. What kind of adventures will they take on?","zh":"\u300a\u4eba\u95f4\u6709\u795e\u517d\uff0c\u6765\u81ea\u4e5d\u91cd\u5929 \u300b\n\n\u968f\u7740\u79d1\u6280\u7684\u53d1\u5c55\uff0c\u5f80\u65e5\u5a01\u98ce\u51db\u51db\u7684\u795e\u517d\u4eec\u65e5\u5b50\u5927\u4e0d\u5982\u524d\u3002\u795e\u517d\u56db\u4e0d\u50cf\u5949\u547d\u4e0b\u51e1\uff0c\u53bb\u89e3\u6551\u6d41\u843d\u4eba\u95f4\u7684\u843d\u9b44\u795e\u517d\u3002\u5728\u51e1\u95f4\uff0c\u4ed6\u9047\u5230\u4e86\u8d70\u6295\u65e0\u8def\u7684\u8001\u540c\u4e8b\u5929\u7984\uff0c\u4e0d\u5f97\u5fd7\u7684\u9152\u53cb\u5154\u7237\uff0c\u88ab\u8d2c\u4e0b\u51e1\u7684\u91d1\u94f6\u89d2\u5144\u5f1f\u2026\u2026\u4ece\u6b64\u5f00\u542f\u4e86\u4e00\u6bb5\u65b0\u7684\u65c5\u7a0b\u3002","es-la":"\"En este reino, criaturas mitol\u00f3gicas deambulan, descendientes de los nueve cielos que llaman hogar.\"\nSibuxiang, un hombre-ciervo mitol\u00f3gico y perezoso, es expulsado del cielo y asignado a apoyar a las criaturas mitol\u00f3gicas que vagan por el mundo humano. Conoce y vive aventuras con sus amigos: el en\u00e9rgico Pixiu amante de la comida llamado Pipi, el fan\u00e1tico conejo lunar Tony, los hermanos ratones Jinjiao y Yinjiao, tambi\u00e9n desterrados del cielo, y muchos otros. \u00bfQu\u00e9 tipo de aventuras emprender\u00e1n?","pt-br":"\"Neste reino, criaturas mitol\u00f3gicas vagam, descendentes dos nove c\u00e9us que chamam de lar.\u201d\n\nSibuxiang, um m\u00edtico homem-cervo pregui\u00e7oso, \u00e9 expulso do c\u00e9u e recebe a miss\u00e3o de ajudar as criaturas mitol\u00f3gicas que vagam pelo mundo humano. Ele conhece e vive aventuras com seus amigos: o energ\u00e9tico e faminto Pixiu chamado Pipi, o fan\u00e1tico coelho da Lua, Tuye, os irm\u00e3os ratos banidos do c\u00e9u Jinjiao e Yinjiao, e muitos outros. Que tipo de aventuras eles viver\u00e3o?"},"isLocked":false,"links":{"al":"131253","ap":"there-are-beasts","kt":"you-shou-yan","mu":"2bhneix","mal":"159325","raw":"https:\/\/manga.bilibili.com\/detail\/mc29329"},"officialLinks":null,"originalLanguage":"zh","lastVolume":null,"lastChapter":null,"publicationDemographic":null,"status":"ongoing","year":2017,"contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"3de8c75d-8ee3-48ff-98ee-e20a65c86451","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Animals"},"description":{},"group":"theme","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"3e2b8dae-350e-4ab8-a8ce-016e844b9f0d","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Long Strip"},"description":{},"group":"format","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"4d32cc48-9f00-4cca-9b5a-a839f0764984","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Comedy"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"cdc58593-87dd-415e-bbc0-2ec27bf404cc","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Fantasy"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"e5301a23-ebd9-49dd-a0cb-2add944c7fe9","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Slice of Life"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"